Liverpool Midfielder Joe Cole Joins Lille on Season-Long Loan

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-31T11:50:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/liverpool-midfielder-joe-cole-joins-lille-on-season-long-loan.html
Liverpool midfielder  Joe Cole  has
joined French champion Lille on loan for the rest of the season,
the Premier League club said on its website.  Cole, 29, signed a four-year deal with Liverpool in July
2010 after his contract at Chelsea had expired. He scored three
goals in 32 appearances with the Reds last season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  